No, it's a bad rip. 

The little clicks at the beginning of track 1 aren't part of the song, they're glitches. You can even hear the sound pop at around 13s.

QMI released an mp3 rerip of cd1 to fix it but I haven't seen a rerip of the flac version.

Anyways, just warning peeps that this release isn't perfect like it should be...
